{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "df04439f-f56a-4261-8ff5-bd8f82a48768", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/df04439f-f56a-4261-8ff5-bd8f82a48768@1.pkg/1772597699998/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597701045", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/df04439f-f56a-4261-8ff5-bd8f82a48768@1.pkg/1772597699998/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597701045"}, "identifier": "df04439f-f56a-4261-8ff5-bd8f82a48768", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查集体生活的作用。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①：荣格的这一理论说明我们要在集体协作中不断改进，不断自我完善，因此该选项符合题意。故①正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>②：&ldquo;我+我们=完整的我&rdquo;强调在集体中我们能成为更好的自己，能实现差异互补，促进自身进步，该选项符合题意。故②正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>③：&ldquo;要为集体发展牺牲自我&rdquo;说法错误，在集体生活中我们需要在一定程度上为集体利益适当让步，但不是要我们牺牲自我。因此③错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>④：&ldquo;个体可以脱离集体生存&rdquo;说法错误，集体和个体相辅相成，互不可缺，个体不能离开集体生存。因此④说法错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①②正确，因此选A</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;我+我们=完整的我&rdquo;这是著名心理学家荣格提出的理论。下列说法与该理论相符合的是（　　　）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①在集体中涵养包容品格，在协作中完善自我修养</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②集体平台助力个性发展，差异互补激发个人潜能</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③个体的进步离不开集体，要为集体发展牺牲自我</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④集体的强大离不开个体，个体可以脱离集体生存</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“我+我们=完整的我”这是著名心理学家荣格提出的理论。下列说法与该理论相符合的是（　　　）①在集体中涵养包容品格，在协作中完善自我修养②集体平台助力个性发展，差异互补激发个人潜能③个体的进步离不开集体，要为集体发展牺牲自我④集体的强大离不开个体，个体可以脱离集体生存", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/df04439f-f56a-4261-8ff5-bd8f82a48768@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977940465", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①② &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①③ &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②④ &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;我+我们=完整的我&rdquo;这是著名心理学家荣格提出的理论。下列说法与该理论相符合的是（　　　）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①在集体中涵养包容品格，在协作中完善自我修养</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②集体平台助力个性发展，差异互补激发个人潜能</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③个体的进步离不开集体，要为集体发展牺牲自我</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④集体的强大离不开个体，个体可以脱离集体生存</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "df04439f-f56a-4261-8ff5-bd8f82a48768", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）“我+我们=完整的我”这是著名心理学家荣格提出的理论。下列说法与该理论相符合的是（　　　）①在集体中涵养包容品格，在协作中完善自我修养②集体平台助力个性发展，差异互补激发个人潜能③个体的进步离不开集体，要为集体发展牺牲自我④集体的强大离不开个体，个体可以脱离集体生存"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;我+我们=完整的我&rdquo;这是著名心理学家荣格提出的理论。下列说法与该理论相符合的是（　　　）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①在集体中涵养包容品格，在协作中完善自我修养</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②集体平台助力个性发展，差异互补激发个人潜能</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③个体的进步离不开集体，要为集体发展牺牲自我</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④集体的强大离不开个体，个体可以脱离集体生存</span></p></div>"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"questio